scenes.description: Performance of 'Dramatic XViltration' by Moona Hoshinova, Ayunda Risu, and Airani Iofifteen.
Transition section with audience cheering as the performers leave the stage and new ones prepare.
Performance of 'Seishun Archive' by Tsunomaki Watame and Tokoyami Towa.

subtitles.original: 我らの蘇り
subtitles.english: Our resurrection

subtitles.original: 鏡に映る
subtitles.english: Reflected in the mirror

subtitles.original: 心に宿っている
subtitles.english: Residing in the heart

subtitles.original: 小さい光
subtitles.english: A small light

subtitles.original: さあ　今も感じる
subtitles.english: Come, I still feel it

subtitles.original: どこか心の奥で
subtitles.english: Somewhere deep in my heart

subtitles.original: 呼び覚ました
subtitles.english: Awakened

subtitles.original: 忘れられない浮かぶメモリ
subtitles.english: Unforgettable memories surfacing

subtitles.original: 今の自分になるその前に
subtitles.english: Before I become who I am now

subtitles.original: 果てのない音色で迷い
subtitles.english: Getting lost in an endless melody

subtitles.original: そして黄昏が落ちてくるどこまでも
subtitles.english: And the twilight falls, wherever it may be

subtitles.original: 引き締める鎖がまた　体を止めていた
subtitles.english: The tightening chains had stopped my body again

subtitles.original: 躊躇い覚えてしまって　凍えていくの
subtitles.english: Having learned hesitation, I am freezing

subtitles.original: 明日の向こう側には　未知なるエリア
subtitles.english: Beyond tomorrow lies an unknown area

subtitles.original: その境界線の先に待つのは
subtitles.english: What awaits beyond that boundary line

subtitles.original: 壱語のはじめ
subtitles.english: The beginning of the first word

subtitles.original: 目覚めは鳴らす
subtitles.english: Awakening rings out

subtitles.original: 奈落の底へと　落ちていく
subtitles.english: Falling to the bottom of the abyss

subtitles.original: 知覚さえ知らぬ
subtitles.english: Unaware even of perception

subtitles.original: 時計の針の音
subtitles.english: The sound of the clock hands

subtitles.original: 頼りなく残り
subtitles.english: Weakly remaining

subtitles.original: 広がる海
subtitles.english: The spreading sea

subtitles.original: 届くはずのない　知らない森の中に
subtitles.english: Inside an unknown forest that shouldn't be reachable

subtitles.original: 宇宙を超え　逃げ場探して
subtitles.english: Beyond space, searching for a place to escape

subtitles.original: そんな過去もまだ　頭に響いている
subtitles.english: Such a past as well, still echoing in my head

subtitles.original: 解けない鎖を断ち　切れないまま足掻き
subtitles.english: Breaking unbreakable chains, struggling while unable to sever them

subtitles.original: 物語の始まり　探し続けたい
subtitles.english: The beginning of the story, I want to keep searching for it

subtitles.original: 無情　一度きりの不甲斐ない　謎のようなことさ
subtitles.english: Heartlessness, a one-time, pathetic, mystery-like thing

subtitles.original: この体の中で目覚めた
subtitles.english: Awakened inside this body

subtitles.original: 本当の姿
subtitles.english: My true form

subtitles.original: 運命のカードが占う未来
subtitles.english: The future predicted by the cards of fate

subtitles.original: 深層へ
subtitles.english: To the depths

subtitles.original: おまじない
subtitles.english: Incantation

subtitles.original: 解き放つ鎖が消え　進めると信じて
subtitles.english: The chains that set me free disappear, believing I can move forward

subtitles.original: 新しい自分になって　光の方へ
subtitles.english: Becoming a new me, towards the light

subtitles.original: 遂に辿り着いた　未知なるエリア
subtitles.english: Finally reached the unknown area

subtitles.original: その境界線を超える日が来た
subtitles.english: The day to cross that boundary has come

subtitles.original: 壱語の終わり
subtitles.english: The end of the first word

subtitles.original: 信じ合う仲間と一緒に
subtitles.english: Together with friends who believe in each other

subtitles.original: 挑戦の狼煙を上げよう
subtitles.english: Let's raise the signal fire of challenge

subtitles.original: 終わらない　青春アーカイブ
subtitles.english: Never-ending Seishun Archive

subtitles.original: 凡人なんて自称は捨てて　兵児！
subtitles.english: Discard the self-proclaimed title of an ordinary person, Hey!

subtitles.original: みんなで揃えば行けるじゃん
subtitles.english: If we're all together, we can go, can't we?
